{"tid":1428370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應對鐳射鎗記招","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:54:43.000Z","uid":706,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"abfcc55cf1d7aae3d6b8e30c2e00083455c2d05e","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"首先唔應該針對佢今日present既手法<br />\n一黎 講科學原理對無腦既人黎講太複雜<br />\n二黎 根本問題就係單憑件物件有危險性就要拉係完全唔合理，依個先係重點<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以搵人拍段片 (大J？)<br />\n標題同一開始就引人入去，話雷射鎗真係好危險<br />\n然後就話其實仲有好多其他危險物品應該要拉<br />\n跟住攞枝無開蓋既筆插穿紙<br />\n打火機點煙<br />\n豬肉刀切豬肉<br />\n然後就話，係喎，你條J都可以用黎強姦有危險性喎<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">帶出重點: 單憑物品有危險性就拉係完全不合理<br />\n</span><br />\n最後片尾要嘲諷信既人，竟然信毫無學識既毅進仔，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所謂好仔唔當差，幾十年前已經講緊啦！<br />\n令到班廢老就恥與為伍，道理就好似之前有巴打話&rdquo;廢老先睇CCTVB&rdquo;一樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知無可能每一次都反擊，但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">趁住依家黑警聲譽又創新低，一定要踩多兩腳，務求令佢以後講乜都無人信</span></span><br />\n<br />\n認同請推，謝謝"},{"pid":"e555d6e8d62b15d6e23d2e32dd52e05e23544fec","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"頭一兩次一定要回應，仲要兜巴收佢皮<br />\n唔可以比機會啲廢老同中立人士相信，以為我地真係理虧<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">只要收佢地一兩次皮之後，以後唔會再有人進佢地，我地亦唔需要再擔心被抹黑</span></span><br />\n所以懇求大家考慮我意見，或者有其他更好方法都無所謂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點係今次一定要完全令佢地再無口實，對準問題根源，拆穿佢地，唔好討論佢地記者會既手法問題，咁樣只會被Spin同離根本問題越黎越遠</span></span>"},{"pid":"47e26c1ca4033d0524616f105647d32400df9067","tid":1428370,"uid":21965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"有得諗喎"},{"pid":"c44492932ebced703186de0b3c122c626e9480bb","tid":1428370,"uid":21965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"推俾文宣組"},{"pid":"67ccc74ba6f2beea4b0503fbbad2653d82e81340","tid":1428370,"uid":21965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"推俾識整片嘅巴絲"},{"pid":"cc5a64db023c605046bf57d9c21d65e760bafd7b","tid":1428370,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"呢兩日記者會已經睇得出最易攻陷果個就係姓江條茂利，最沉唔住氣最易講錯野，不過要記者專攻呢條柒頭先得"},{"pid":"7bb9ef1908334b2d94a70b7c02536be471d699f4","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:01:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85fcee8278cd6fbd7a77b0a83b5bec367ce01a96","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:09:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8788748b01268151820cb8ae6f31553a6be2757a","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50d38e20fe3a16a53f62b767f21cc3245c899759","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95cca9892b29ecd6644b5b6d432560ccf4a0b798","tid":1428370,"uid":265047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba33b53859f6a9d1c3b7ec00c2cecd5084d65061","tid":1428370,"uid":255934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"推俾大j 睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816060960655a212c953291adb2d8ade200c85de","tid":1428370,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"一定要正面拆 講觀星筆其實係日常用品 仲有解釋佢個實驗唔合理既地方 仲有好多日常用品做到同樣效果"},{"pid":"7da531adbd9f24591eccdbd5