fe783cd1338db","tid":1428370,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:21:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電筒/ laser pointer 唔係能量問題</span><br />\n<br />\n係警方無任何理據去拉人，<br />\n<br />\n1.佢唔係示威現場<br />\n2.佢無用黎射過任何野<br />\n3.無任何公告招集用黎射人<br />\n<br />\n佢只係一個買laser 的人，並唔構成任何理據拘捕<br />\n<br />\n無論你點樣諗佢動機，你無表面証據就收皮。<br />\n<br />\n我理得你支 laser 射爆月球，法治就係法治"},{"pid":"6df7d295078aab75ba7892688edb553210c4948e","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bec3814615212a50a685a377cb6caf0c6cc0470","tid":1428370,"uid":158166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8cf95e9b618ca6f6177bacafd31a72e8d4dd2cb","tid":1428370,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我建議文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"778ab995de0123bc923989e609900d609cfae1b9","tid":1428370,"uid":12166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"小心cctvb 特燈用學事學非東張去抹黑"},{"pid":"38b12fcdfbb92d9ba138eb6dcdde1a5d308682ac","tid":1428370,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用另一件更加大，更加有殺傷力嘅文宣攻擊<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾佢帶住輿論呀！<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f2b9462ba8e83e5ca4a92578e9e4d13a53f34149","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"778ab995de0123bc923989e609900d609cfae1b9","tid":1428370,"uid":12166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:23:56.000Z","msg":"小心cctvb 特燈用學事學非東張去抹黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"所以一定要撥亂反正，帶返啲人既思維去正途<br />\n講多次<span style=\"color: red;\">重點唔係如何推論件物品有危險性，而係單憑件物品既危險性去拉人係完全不合理</span>"},{"pid":"fe82ea32bca3941de067825fe346a675bed78372","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55a32eb516890fd40e085a60604100cfbe38a949","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c95410956c420d5fb37dfc13a9cbe67d1da506fb","tid":1428370,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"其實係要拆解佢個實驗根本無厘頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係要佢證明浸大學生會會長係有意圖買支野傷害人呀DLLM<br />\n有左呢個先例買把菜刀拎番屋企切生菜都唔得啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"4562fa965db1af27cae5d9c4a87faa36147527ff","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c95410956c420d5fb37dfc13a9cbe67d1da506fb","tid":1428370,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"其實係要拆解佢個實驗根本無厘頭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係要佢證明浸大學生會會長係有意圖買支野傷害人呀DLLM<br />\n有左呢個先例買把菜刀拎番屋企切生菜都唔得啦</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"你係無睇內文定係個腦有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"74b67db7ce1773d793f47f893f2da58409a80324","tid":1428370,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fa7421f0bef70833a85c9d7542bddfe4a1a2dda","tid":1428370,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4